        {
          "ri": 17,
          "rowText": "Diagnosis Pri* NA J02 - Acute pharyngitis J01 - Acute sinusitis J03 - Acute tonsillitis J069 - Acute upper respiratory infection J304 - Allergic rhinitis T784 - Allergy L63 - Alopecia areata I726 - Aneurysm and dissection of vertebral artery K120 - Apthous mouth ulcers J45 - Asthma L20 - Atopic dermatitis G510 - Bells palsy N20.2 - Calculus of kidney with calculus of ureter L03 - Cellulitis H001 - Chalazion R074 - Chest pain, unspecified B01 - Chicken pox infections M224 - Chondromalacia patellae ICD-N18 - Chronic kidney disease (CKD) E10 - Diabetes Mellitus (insulin dep.) E11 - Diabetes Mellitus (non-insul. dep.) R42 - Dizziness and giddiness I10 - Essential (primary) hypertension Z013 - Examination of blood pressure L26 - Exfoliative dermatitis R50 - Fever of unknown origin K29 - Gastritis and duodenitis K297 - Gastritis, unspecified K21 - Gastro-oesophageal reflux disease A09 - Gastroenteritis M10 - Gout R51 - Headache G442 - Headache (tension type) B980 - Helicobacter pylori [H.pylori] infection (opportunistic) as cause of diseas E785 - Hyperlipidaemia E790 - Hyperuricaemia J11 - Influenza, virus not identified M545 - Low back pain (Loin pain; Low back strain; Lumbago NOS) G43 - Migraine H041 - Other disorders of lacrimal gland G258 - Other extrapyramidal/movement disorders(incl Restless legs/Stiff-man syndro H60 - Otitis externa R101 - Pain localized to upper abdomen (Epigastric pain) N944 - Primary dysmenorrhoea R21 - Rash & other nonspec. skin erupt. J12.81 - SARS associated coronavirus (wuhan) S934 - Sprain and strain of ankle A155 - Tuberculosis of larynx, trachea and bronchus, confirmed bacteriologically N390 - Urinary tract infection L50 - Urticaria I861 - VARICOCELE SCROTUM B30 - Viral conjunctivitis E539 - Vitamin B deficiency, unspecified",
